{"tid":1597734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立法會明起至10.1封天橋入口 未來數日倘衝突或發紅色警示","createTime":"2019-09-27T05:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T07:18:27.000Z","uid":68738,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a97bc335065275987594e18e54342c2f4dacac5f","tid":1597734,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"反修例運動引發一連串警民衝突，三個月以來，立法會大樓和政府總部，多次成為示威者包圍對象。立法會秘書處宣佈，由明日（28日）起關閉立法會1樓天橋入口，預料十一後才會重開。秘書處指未來數日立法會外有機會發生衝突，會按情況安排警員於立法會大樓內外侯勤。而持有長期證件的傳媒如要進入大樓，則須經地面入口，且提供身分證作登記。<br />\n<br />\n秘書處並稱如發生暴力衝突，將考慮徵詢行管會主席等人後發出紅色警示，屆時所有人均須離開立法會大樓，警員亦會進駐大樓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190927/60090082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190927%2F60090082&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYv3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=60a62b8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190927%2F60090082&h=b1ecaa36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190927/60090082</a>"},{"pid":"a28bc23ef8acd5297a6e7715dea07a34bcfcebf9","tid":1597734,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a0a5c28be764cce545fc51a4803eeb335b1dca","tid":1597734,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T05:42:27.000Z","msg":"屆時所有人均須離開立法會大樓，警員亦會進駐大樓。<br />\n軍政府正式奪權<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86bdf16c24581c9270c8a898c53fa1d46e015e7","tid":1597734,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{